Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他們別惹出什麼麻煩來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:28.21,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,600)\pos(575,250)}後山入口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡將會是血流成河的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你這種人該來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就祝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得開心留下一份美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  天知道會變成多奇葩的野餐會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啦  音無
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  你可別第一個就被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這地方不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要不在這玩一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去把野餐布鋪好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫下忙  大山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不被風吹走  在四個角都放上石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有野餐的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就這麼躺著看天空也非常舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We  love  the  earth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是死後的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們玩什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多人  要不玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下五段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然中計了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  高松  這是你弄的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我去拜託Guild一週就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為Attacker  Killer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠直白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了什麼啊  高松
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不就是這樣的作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓我們其中一人化身成惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要相互廝殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又是第一個被幹掉  野田那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼活下來的人就繼續玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又有什麼鬼主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來打羽毛球吧  我帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  帶我來這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚子也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想趁這個機會  向岩澤前輩請教點音樂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們邊走邊說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩澤前輩是因為什麼才開始搞音樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最開始讓我感到震撼的是個叫SAD  MACHINE的樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  我們成功了  美雪親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後會很恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫SAD  MACHINE的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他的聲音非常高調  震耳欲聾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對於當時的我來說  就像是救贖之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有第二個陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界見到尚子的時候  我感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次肯定成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到了相同的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以生前是因為SAD  MACHINE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而來到這個世界後則是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次給我帶來電吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直陪伴著我的尚子  讓我繼續著音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要發球了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該抽殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three  love  year  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  大山你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦到了  我辦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把高松君給…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭啊  委託科學部製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載了火箭引擎的特製球拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為Receiver  Crasher
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學部好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了這種事情居然還能這麼平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要責怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你把高松幹掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是決定惡魔的作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說是看到高松君委託別人製作炸彈排球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想到原來還有這麼一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是做了相同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能只責備大山一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的開什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山  只有你的提議我不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去河邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才去看了一下  這附近有一條河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很適合釣魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去釣魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去釣魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有個性的他  會變得這麼活躍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I  hate  folk
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無別看  不能看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下五段也被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我拜託園藝部製作的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也弄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且園藝部好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會變成這麼厲害的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本只想模仿電影裡的一幕  沒想到完美再現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不必太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神去釣魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是剛剛才吐過  振作得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太有個性了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個大傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  是大傢伙的話我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手沒法鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是知道的吧  我是個旱鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺住  這就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go  to  barrier  club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花樣游泳部好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼淺都能溺水也真服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釣竿被動過手腳也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是松下五段所設的陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你這麼一說的確是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說還會有大家設下的陷阱咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我已經厭煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  那是我委託遙控模型部做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有逃跑了  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非得因為你設下的陷阱而拼命逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說抱歉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個氣味是汽油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙控模型部好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想到會做到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時那女孩正在機場大廳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對漫畫部  Be  careful
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手伸過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳被纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釣魚部和花樣游泳部的配合好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  現在不是佩服的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這應該就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  日向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還有這種陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫畫部好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩我一個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  謹慎點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼岩澤她們一聲不吭就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪親  接下來是魔之五連坑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能挺過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要在這次作戰裡完成以下犯上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  能問一下作曲有什麼竅門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？  對作曲感興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過用貝斯來作曲似乎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過用貝斯來作曲似乎有點難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟不太彈和弦  只用根音的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能不明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  把我的吉他借給你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以回憶中的吉他為原型…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guild的人為我製作的複製品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表簡直一模一樣  雖…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然泛音稍淡了一些  不過還是很不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guild的成員現在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連魔之五連坑都不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對音樂究竟是有多癡迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  臉色那麼蒼白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒沒沒  請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的陷阱是「岩澤前輩惡魔化計畫」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個還是算了吧  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要用那個讓岩澤前輩變成惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她成為天使的餌食
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是以下犯上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下犯上？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒沒沒  請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:36.58,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,220)\an5}作戰{\1a&ff&\t(500,501,\1a&00&)}實施{\1a&ff&\t(1000,1001,\1a&00&)}三天前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.58,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.58,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當了個然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  先攪拌一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色有點樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個只會說「是呢」這句話的機器人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  「是呢」應該是我今天第一次說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不小心條件反射吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入生肝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實吧  真的需要做到這個地步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想想我們一直點生肝是為了什麼  美雪親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己就別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼最後為了弄出黏稠感加一些澱粉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是這聞起來的氣味  和血一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個實在是有點不妥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就標注過「本作品含有暴力以及血腥場景」了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒再補上個「請絕對不要模仿」就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:07.38,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\pos(322,355)}※請絕對不要模仿。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幫那隻小狗找個女伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是綁了個髮帶上去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能在這次的作戰中協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無  GDM成員之外全部陣亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guild降落作戰的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙作為一個新人  還挺能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便過了幾十年  眼光還是那麼毒辣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還活著早就老太婆了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這類事情以後不許提
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我現在朝現場趕去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候大駕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.46,0:23:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來能到那邊去聊聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說岩澤怎麼全身破破爛爛的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.55,0:23:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:23:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尚子前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:02.26,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對岩澤做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  不能靠近那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連尚子前輩也掉進陷阱裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下捅大婁子了  美雪親喲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.54,0:24:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽到了尚子的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  在  這  裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是關根你搞的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒戲了  作戰失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪親  我先溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.97,0:24:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起溜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.81,0:24:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.89,0:24:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  尚子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.03,0:24:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.32,0:25:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在餵她吃什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.77,0:25:32.33,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\pos(322,355)}※之後由工作人員美味地享用了。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.02,0:25:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.85,0:25:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個天使竟然在動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.96,0:25:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界終於誕生除天使外的另一種非人物種了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.72,0:25:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅身為使者的你是贏不了她的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.59,0:25:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把神叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.33,0:26:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣的作戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.47,0:26:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道事情的經過
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.02,0:26:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個樣子確實是惡魔沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.09,0:26:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.71,0:26:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.66,0:26:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊神  快把神叫來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.93,0:26:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.77,0:26:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於現世了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.43,0:26:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的右手隱隱作痛也是因為這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.10,0:26:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿於我身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.54,0:26:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,✟ hand·sonic ✟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.07,0:26:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至今為止有那種出招台詞？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.68,0:26:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點中二
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.25,0:26:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將你再次封入第三世界
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.98,0:26:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很中二
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.01,0:27:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.88,0:27:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.21,0:27:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.43,0:27:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連領袖都不放過？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪是什麼惡魔  完全就是個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.41,0:27:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.91,0:27:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老身的樂隊名成了Girls  Dead  Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.93,0:27:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.50,0:27:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  老身也差不多要離去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.07,0:27:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.13,0:27:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說我也是女生  這提問太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.12,0:27:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去廁所吧  走好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.13,0:28:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.13,0:28:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些生肝究竟是腐壞到什麼程度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.53,0:28:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.85,0:28:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.96,0:29:47.75,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\pos(600,210)\fad(100,0)}再會
